One lucky reader of the Daily Dispatch will take home a stylish new trailer from Getaway trailers. To stand a chance of winning simply get a copy of the Daily Dispatch and fill in the entry form, which is printed in the newspaper every day. The more times you enter, the better your chances are of winning. Hurry, because entries close on 1 April 2022. Entries can be delivered to Getaway trailers in Beacon Bay, or any Daily Dispatch satellite office including the Daily Dispatch offices in Quenera Drive, Beacon Bay; The Ink Spot in Mthatha; or The Rep office in Queenstown. Entry boxes will also be available in selected retail stores throughout our the Daily Dispatch distribution area, and wherever our win-a-trailer promoters are present. How will I know if I am a winner? The winner will be announced in the Daily Dispatch newspaper on Friday, 8 April 2022, and the trailer will be handed over to the lucky winner on Thursday, 14 April 2022